                              <p class="font_8">
                               ·  Join us at Fellowship Bible Church – Our Women’s Ministry will be showing the God of Creation Bible study videos and hosting a discussion time weekly on Wednesday evenings, 6:30-8:30pm, Room 212, beginning June 27th.
                              </p>
                              <p class="font_8">
                               ·  We will view the weekly video and discuss it the first week. The following weeks we will discuss the homework first, then view the video and discuss it.
                              </p>
                              <p class="font_8">
                               ·  God of Creation is 10 weeks long. If you miss a week with us, you can view the video at home from the Lifeway link below.
                              </p>

                               ·  You’ll need to purchase a God Of Creation workbook, $12.99 at the
